Gifts of the spirit are universally needed to be used like the parable of the talent.


THEY ARE

NOT

A Ministry.

Any christian can prophesy, word of wisdom or talk in tounges. All should use those God Given gifts.



An evangelist ministry can use the gift of prophesy just like the prophet ministry 

but

Those ministries have different functions as per the bible standards.

I love you all - Father God via tounges.



